Package: safetysignal
Title: Bayesian Gamma-Poisson Signal Detection for Pharmacovigilance
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Harlan", "Nelson", , "hnelson3@iuhealth.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Multi-item Gamma-Poisson Shrinker (MGPS) for
    detecting disproportionate reporting of adverse events in spontaneous
    reporting systems (FAERS, VAERS, MAUDE). Uses a 2-component Gamma
    mixture prior fitted via EM algorithm, with full posterior percentiles
    for signal detection.
